# Group Categories

## Browse Categories [/browse/categories{?locale,limit,offset}]

### getcategories [GET]
Get a list of categories used to tag items in Spotify (on, for example, the Spotify player’s “Browse” tab).
+ Parameters
    + locale (string, optional)

        + Sample: sv_SE
    + limit (number, optional) -

        + Default: 20
        + Sample: 10
    + offset (number, optional) -

        + Default: 0
        + Sample: 5

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        A paged set of categories

    + Attributes (PagedCategories)



+ Response 401 (application/json)

        Bad or expired token. This can happen if the user revoked a token or
the access token has expired. You should re-authenticate the user.

    + Attributes (Unauthorized1)



+ Response 403 (application/json)

        Bad OAuth request (wrong consumer key, bad nonce, expired
timestamp...). Unfortunately, re-authenticating the user won't help here.

    + Attributes (Forbidden1)



+ Response 429 (application/json)

        The app has exceeded its rate limits.

    + Attributes (TooManyRequests1)




## Browse Categories By Category Id [/browse/categories/{category_id}{?locale}]

+ Parameters
    + category_id (string, required)

        + Sample: dinner

### getacategory [GET]
Get a single category used to tag items in Spotify (on, for example, the Spotify player’s “Browse” tab).
+ Parameters
    + locale (string, optional)

        + Sample: sv_SE

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        A category

    + Attributes (CategoryObject)



+ Response 401 (application/json)

        Bad or expired token. This can happen if the user revoked a token or
the access token has expired. You should re-authenticate the user.

    + Attributes (Unauthorized1)



+ Response 403 (application/json)

        Bad OAuth request (wrong consumer key, bad nonce, expired
timestamp...). Unfortunately, re-authenticating the user won't help here.

    + Attributes (Forbidden1)



+ Response 429 (application/json)

        The app has exceeded its rate limits.

    + Attributes (TooManyRequests1)





