# Group Search

## Search [/search{?q,type,market,limit,offset,include_external}]

### search [GET]
Get Spotify catalog information about albums, artists, playlists, tracks, shows, episodes or audiobooks
that match a keyword string. Audiobooks are only available within the US, UK, Canada, Ireland, New Zealand and Australia markets.
+ Parameters
    + q (string, required)

        + Sample: remaster%20track:Doxy%20artist:Miles%20Davis
    + type (array[string], required)

        + Members
            + `album` 
            + `artist` 
            + `playlist` 
            + `track` 
            + `show` 
            + `episode` 
            + `audiobook` 

    + market (string, optional)

        + Sample: ES
    + limit (number, optional) -

        + Default: 20
        + Sample: 10
    + offset (number, optional) -

        + Default: 0
        + Sample: 5
    + include_external (enum[string], optional)

        + Members
            + `audio` 


+ Response 200 (application/json)

        Search response

    + Attributes (SearchItems)



+ Response 401 (application/json)

        Bad or expired token. This can happen if the user revoked a token or
the access token has expired. You should re-authenticate the user.

    + Attributes (Unauthorized1)



+ Response 403 (application/json)

        Bad OAuth request (wrong consumer key, bad nonce, expired
timestamp...). Unfortunately, re-authenticating the user won't help here.

    + Attributes (Forbidden1)



+ Response 429 (application/json)

        The app has exceeded its rate limits.

    + Attributes (TooManyRequests1)





